features: 【STRONG AND RUST-FREE】Made of premium 304 stainless steel, our roll up dish drying rack is very strong and rustless, and ensures long-time use.
【UPGRADE LARGE SIZE】Our dish drying rack is 18’’ x 13’’ and suitable for most kitchen sinks, and our tank rack can safely hold 88 pounds and 450 ℉of heat.
【ALL IS FOR YOUR WORRY】Made of food-grade silicone, the edges are soft and non-slip, which prevents rack from slipping and any wear to your sink.
【ALL KITCHENWARES ARE READY】Our roll up drain rack can be used for air-drying washed bowls, pot, fry pans, and cutlery and even to dry washed fruits and vegetables.
【AS EASY AS PIE TO STORE】Our dish drying mat is foldable and can be rolled up for easy storage. Simple and stylish design makes your kitchen cleaner and more luxurious.
